high_descs: Go straight and to the left to in between the wall and the coffee table, face the coffee table.
Take the lap top from the coffee table.
Turn to the right.
Put the lap top on the right side of the foot stool.
Turn left, go straight to the couch, move left to face the left couch cushion.
Take the lap top from the left couch cushion.
Turn around, go straight, turn left, go towards the foot stool.
Put the lap top on the left side of the foot stool
anns.task_desc: Put 2 lap tops on a foot stool

high_descs: Go past the TV on the right to between the wall and coffee table.
Pick up the laptop on the table.
Turn to face the chair.
Set the laptop down on the foot rest.
Go between the coffee table and foot rest to the couch.
Pick up the laptop on the couch.
Go to the foot rest in front of the chair.
Set the laptop down on the foot rest.
anns.task_desc: Put two laptops on the foot rest.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the coffee table with laptop on it.
Pick up the laptop from the table.
Turn right and walk to the blue ottoman.
Put the laptop on the ottoman.
Turn left, turn left again, walk to blue couch with laptop on it, turn to face couch.
Pick up laptop from the couch.
Turn left, turn left again, walk past coffee table, make another left, walk to ottoman.
Place laptop on ottoman to left of other laptop and perpendicular to it.
Turn left, turn right, walk along the coffee table to where the laptop is, turn left to face it.
Pick up laptop from coffee table.
Turn right, walk to the ottoman.
Put down the laptop on the ottoman.
Turn left, walk past the coffee table, turn left, walk to the far end of the couch.
Pick up the laptop from the couch.
Turn left, turn left, walk to the corner of the coffee table, turn left, walk to ottoman.
Put the laptop on the ottoman to the left of the other laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put two laptops on the ottoman.
